# Advanced Shopify Theme Development Guidelines

## **Design System Integration Requirements**

### **Design Thinking Framework Application**
```javascript
// ✅ DO: Apply design thinking methodology for UI decisions
// Invoke: @design-thinking-framework-rules.mdc
class ThemeDesignProcess {
  constructor() {
    this.empathyPhase = new EmpathyPhase();
    this.problemDefinition = new ProblemDefinition();
    this.ideationPhase = new IdeationPhase();
    this.prototyping = new PrototypingPhase();
  }
  
  async designFeature(featureRequirements) {
    // 1. Empathy: Understand user needs
    const userInsights = await this.empathyPhase.conductUserResearch(featureRequirements);
    
    // 2. Define: Articulate the problem
    const problemStatement = await this.problemDefinition.defineChallenge(userInsights);
    
    // 3. Ideate: Generate solutions
    const solutions = await this.ideationPhase.brainstormSolutions(problemStatement);
    
    // 4. Prototype: Create and test
    const prototype = await this.prototyping.createPrototype(solutions);
    
    return prototype;
  }
}
```

